# Better-Auth User Creation Examples

## Valid User Registration Request
```json
{
  "email": "johndoe@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!",
  "profile": {
    "name": "John Doe",
    "age": 25,
    "role": "student"
  }
}
```

## Valid Response
```json
{
  "result": {
    "success": true,
    "message": "User created successfully",
    "user_id": "user_abc123def456"
  }
}
```

## Error Responses

### Duplicate Email
```json
{
  "result": {
    "success": false,
    "message": "Email already exists",
    "user_id": null
  }
}
```

### Weak Password
```json
{
  "result": {
    "success": false,
    "message": "Validation error: Password must be at least 8 characters",
    "user_id": null
  }
}
```

### API Failure
```json
{
  "result": {
    "success": false,
    "message": "API error: 500 - Internal server error",
    "user_id": null
  }
}
```